            "name": "Greater Shadow",
            "type": "section",
            "text": "Shadows that spend long amounts of time on the Shadow Plane and absorb its magic become greater shadows.<br/><br/><b><u><a aonid=\"5\" game-obj=\"Skills\" general=\"true\">Recall Knowledge - Undead</a></u> (<u><a aonid=\"13\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Religion</a></u>)</b>: DC 23",
